            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD had recommended <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2283.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Friedrich Hildebrand’s</ref> monograph on sexual division in plants (Hildebrand 1867a) in his <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6379.xml" resp="#automat" cert="medium">letter to Farrer of 19 September [1868]</ref>.</note>
